Description: local network client daemon, GTK desktop controller, and terminal dashboard
 clambhook provides a local network client daemon, HTTP control API, and a
 native GTK/libadwaita desktop controller (Wayland with X11 fallback) plus a
 terminal dashboard. It includes a private license helper used by the desktop
 app for trial and license activation against the hosted store backend.
